{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Immerse Yourself in Erannorth - Where Myths Meet Card Strategy!</h2><br>Dive into an alternative Earth where all the legends come alive. Erannorth Chronicles blends old-school card games with intricate RPG elements, set against a backdrop of steampunk wonders. Customization is your playground, and strategy is your weapon. Are you ready to craft your legend?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The World of Erannorth Awaits:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unleash Your Imagination: Navigate an expansive sandbox universe teeming with challenges, treasures, and endless adventures. No scripted story \u2013 just you and a world waiting to be explored.<br></li><li>Master Deck Strategy: Boasting over <strong>4300</strong> collectible cards, the deck-building possibilities are boundless. Adjust, switch, and experiment to outwit <strong>500</strong> unique, ever-evolving enemies.<br></li><li>Craft Your Legend: Choose from 13 Organizations, 15 Species, and 15 Classes to create your hero. With over 100 specializations, no two adventures will ever be the same.<br></li><li>Thriving Mod Community: With full modding and Steam Workshop support, the only limit is your imagination. From tweaking game modes to inserting your artwork, personalizing Erannorth is as easy as editing a text file. Modding has never been this effortless!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Slaver's Den","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1580800/c61114ad61e1393c3be8d3a8d53b69c13e700e42.jpg"},{"name":"What Lies Beneath","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1580800/a606f221f437ff0bbdf020b2f541f0f71e6bdec5.jpg"},{"name":"Ascetic Life","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1580800/8b863cddf54c5a9ae013982acecb17b94e16a086.jpg"},{"name":"Crowhelm Burrow","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1580800/847262df6a1b725b55b5